query:
INSERT INTO
    ais_vessels (
        mmsi,
        imo_number,
        call_sign,
        NAME,
        ship_width,
        ship_length,
        ship_type,
        eta,
        draught,
        destination
    )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],
        $2::INT[],
        $3::VARCHAR[],
        $4::VARCHAR[],
        $5::INT[],
        $6::INT[],
        $7::INT[],
        $8::timestamptz[],
        $9::INT[],
        $10::VARCHAR[]
    )
ON CONFLICT (mmsi) DO
UPDATE
SET
    imo_number = excluded.imo_number,
    call_sign = excluded.call_sign,
    NAME = excluded.name,
    ship_width = excluded.ship_width,
    ship_length = excluded.ship_length,
    ship_type = excluded.ship_type,
    eta = excluded.eta,
    draught = excluded.draught,
    destination = excluded.destination
